snippet.textDisplay: You actually can have the Chinese mass produce high quality knockoffs made to order. It's a myth that they don't have the know-how to make quality knockoffs. The level of quality YOU want is dependent on how much you want to spend. They will mass produce high quality or low quality products to fit your budget. Yes, it's fraudulent but many of the products on ebay are fakes.
